# cozy

surf the small web – a gemini, spartan and nex browser

## cozy navigation

* ctrl-s to visit a spartan space
* ctrl-g to visit a gemini capsule
* ctrl-n to visit a nex station
* ctrl-e to edit the current url
* ctrl-l to follow a link using a shortcut
* ctrl-r to refresh the current page
* ctrl-y to bookmark the current page
* ctrl-o to show bookmarks
* ctrl-h to get back to this page 🙃
* shift-left to go back to the previous page (no forward!)
* . to cancel a request

## cozy arguments

```ksh
$ cozy                  # get cozy
$ cozy blekksprut.net   # head straight to blekksprut.net
$ cozy -b               # edit bookmarks in your editor
$ cozy -t night         # nighttime *all the time*
```

## cozy protocols

=> gemini://geminiprotocol.net/ the gemini protocol
=> nex://nightfall.city/nex/ nex (nightfall express)
=> spartan://spartan.mozz.us spartan (💪)

## cozy bookmarks

bookmarks are stored as a regular gemtext file
new bookmarks are added as new link lines at the end of the file

```
# cozy bookmarks

=> gemini://bbs.geminispace.org/
```

the bookmarks file can be customized to your liking outside of cozy

